      <title>美联储官员柯林斯谈降息可能性、通胀和特朗普</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-15/fed-s-collins-on-possible-rate-cut-inflation-and-trump-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波士顿联邦储备银行行长苏珊·柯林斯表示，12 月降息的可能性不大。柯林斯在接受“彭博未平仓头寸”节目迈克·麦基采访时还就通胀状况、劳动力市场和当选总统唐纳德·特朗普的第二任期发表了评论。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-15/fed-s-collins-on-possible-rate-cut-inflation-and-trump-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Nov 2024 16:12:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
