      <title>俄罗斯暂时限制向美国供应浓缩铀</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-15/russia-temporarily-limits-enriched-uranium-supplies-to-us-m3ivvj3g</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯将暂时限制向美国出口浓缩铀，这将给利用核能发电（占该国近五分之一电力）的公用事业公司带来潜在的供应风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-15/russia-temporarily-limits-enriched-uranium-supplies-to-us-m3ivvj3g</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Nov 2024 15:18:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯天然气工业股份公司停止向奥地利供应天然气，欧洲天然气价格上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-15/omv-says-gazprom-to-suspend-austria-gas-deliveries-on-nov-16</link>
      <description><![CDATA[奥地利石油公司 (OMV AG) 表示俄罗斯将从周六起切断燃料供应，随后欧洲天然气价格上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-15/omv-says-gazprom-to-suspend-austria-gas-deliveries-on-nov-16</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Nov 2024 14:45:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美元上涨势头增强，英镑抹去了今年的涨幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-15/pound-erases-this-year-s-advance-as-dollar-rally-gains-momentum</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于预期美国经济增长和通胀将更加强劲，投资者纷纷买入美元，英镑今年兑美元的升值势头已有所减弱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-15/pound-erases-this-year-s-advance-as-dollar-rally-gains-momentum</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Nov 2024 09:35:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
